    <p>{`High cardinality metric tags can severy disrupt downstream metrics storages. To
protet against this we built a new
`}<a parentName="p" {...{
        "href": "/docs/reference/transforms/tag_cardinality_limit/"
      }}><inlineCode parentName="a">{`tag_cardinality_limit`}</inlineCode>{` transform`}</a>{`.`}</p>
